 - `[^&#39;]*` - zero or more chars other than a `&#39;`
 - `&#39;\]\[scope=&#39;` - a `&#39;][scope=&#39;` string
 - `[^&#39;]*` - zero or more chars other than a `&#39;`
 - `&#39;\]` - a `&#39;]` substring
 - `$` -  end of string.

